  <div class="ex-details">
    <h2>Care That Begins at First Breath</h2>
    <p>Our neonatology programme follows globally recognised protocols for family-centred care. Parents are welcomed into the NICU, kangaroo-mother-care is actively encouraged, and breastfeeding support is offered throughout the stay.</p>
    <p>Beyond the newborn phase, our paediatric team provides continuous care through infancy, toddlerhood, and beyond &mdash; with specialists in general paediatrics, paediatric cardiology, neurology, and developmental care.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Preterm baby care</li>
      <li>Respiratory distress management</li>
      <li>Neonatal jaundice treatment</li>
      <li>Kangaroo mother care</li>
      <li>Immunisation programmes</li>
      <li>Developmental assessment</li>
      <li>Paediatric OPD & emergencies</li>
      <li>Newborn screening panels</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

